      <title>据称西班牙 Sidenor 将收购 Trilantic 在 Talgo 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/spains-sidenor-is-said-make-offer-trilantic-stake-talgo-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位接近谈判的消息人士周一表示，巴斯克钢铁制造商 Sidenor 已提出收购全球投资基金 Trilantic 持有的西班牙火车制造商 Talgo 29.9% 的股份，证实了《Expansion》报早些时候的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/spains-sidenor-is-said-make-offer-trilantic-stake-talgo-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 11:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
