      <title>巴克莱银行放弃对卡塔尔交易的上诉后被英国监管机构罚款 5100 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-financial-regulator-fines-barclays-51-mln-over-disclosures-related-qatar-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融监管机构因巴克莱银行未能披露 2008 年向卡塔尔实体支付的款项而对其处以 4000 万英镑（5090 万美元）罚款。此前该银行周一表示，已放弃对此案的上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/uk-financial-regulator-fines-barclays-51-mln-over-disclosures-related-qatar-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 08:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行首席经济学家称，政策不应维持太长时间</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-lane-monetary-policy-should-not-remain-restrictive-too-long-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩在接受采访时表示，欧元区通胀率要持续回到2%还有一段路要走，但欧洲央行的政策不应持续限制太久，否则价格增长可能低于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecbs-lane-monetary-policy-should-not-remain-restrictive-too-long-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 06:13:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
